		<td><b>Re: I think I found some pirate carts at a local store...</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Any definition is going to fall short somewhere (I personally agree that retrotainment's games ARE homebrew, and tengen's aren't, but how do you draw that line?)<br /><br />I think a more important question is: why do need a pure definition?  What purpose does this delineation serve?<br /><br />Separating homebrews from pirates is helpful to make sure people don't get ripped off by pirated work. Beyond that, I'm not sure that finding a perfect definition is useful.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


